OL,5, Primary school children are targeting  
OL,6, each other with homophobic and         
OL,7, anti-trans abuse, a professor has      
OL,8, warned.                                
OL,10,FCardiff University's EJ Renold said    
OL,11,Fthey had noticed an increase in young  
OL,12,Fchildren reporting homophobic and      
OL,13,Fsexist comments.                       
OL,15,FLast year an Estyn report found        
OL,16,Fhomophobic bullying was the most common
OL,17,Fkind in secondary schools and happened 
OL,18,F"all the time".                        
OL,20,FThe Welsh government said any bullying 
OL,21,Fwas "unacceptable".                    
